Class HLLWritable

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adroll.cantor.HLLWritable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable

    public class HLLWritable
extends Object
implements org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable
    HLLWritable allows for serialization and deserialization of HLLCounter objects in a Hadoop framework.

      • combine

        public HLLWritable combine(HLLWritable other)
        Returns a new HLLWritable that contains a representation of combining its internal HLLCounter's representation with the other's.

        It is functionally equivalent to combining two HLLCounters (HLLCounter.combine(HLLCounter h)) and creating a new HLLWritable out of that.

        Returns null if the combination fails.

        Parameters:
        other - the HLLWritable to combine
        Returns:
        the HLLWritable that represents the union, null if fails, this if other is null.
